item.title: CVE-2022-2146|2024-08-03T00:24:44.217Z -- unknown -- import%20csv%20files
item.description: The Import CSV Files WordPress plugin through 1.0 does not sanitise and escaped imported data before outputting them back in a page, and is lacking CSRF check when performing such action as well, resulting in a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting
